# ThoughtSpot → Databricks Metric View

Convert a ThoughtSpot Worksheet or Model into a Databricks Metric View. Searches
ThoughtSpot for available models, exports the TML definition, maps it to the
Databricks Metric View YAML format, and creates it via
`CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW ... WITH METRICS LANGUAGE YAML AS $$ ... $$`.

Mode A only (single conversion). Single-table models produce v0.1 YAML.

